{% extends "layouts/main.njk" %}
{% from "components/button/macro.njk" import LBCamdenButton %}

{% set pageTitle = "Make a professional referral for mental health social care support" %}

{% block content %}
  <div class="govuk-width-container">
    <div class="govuk-grid-row">
      <div class="govuk-grid-column-two-thirds">
        <span class="govuk-caption-m">Page 0</span>
        <h1 class="govuk-heading-xl">Make a professional referral for mental health social care support</h1>

        <p class="govuk-body">Professionals can refer someone for mental health social care support.</p>
        <p class="govuk-body">Professionals include doctors, nurses, healthcare workers, carers, among others.</p>
        <p class="govuk-body">If you want to get help for someone you know personally, speak to their GP or another professional involved in their care.</p>

        <h2 class="govuk-heading-l">What you can make a referral for</h2>

        <p class="govuk-body">Professionals can ask for help with mental health support for a Camden resident. This includes:</p>

        <ul class="govuk-list govuk-list--bullet">
          <li>social care and support needs assessment</li>
          <li>review of existing package of care</li>
          <li>deep clean or environmental health</li>
          <li>carer support or assessment</li>
        </ul>

        <p class="govuk-body">This referral form is not for:</p>

        <ul class="govuk-list govuk-list--bullet">
          <li>safeguarding concerns, such as abuse or neglect</li>
          <li>signposting to volunteer teams</li>
          <li>befriending or advocacy services. Ideally, professionals should signpost</li>
        </ul>

        <h3 class="govuk-heading-m">Safeguarding</h3>

        <p class="govuk-body">If you have <a class="govuk-link" href="https://camdencarechoices.camden.gov.uk/reporting-abuse-and-staying-safe/what-is-safeguarding-adults/">safeguarding concerns</a> for a Camden resident who may be vulnerable to abuse or neglect, you should not use this form.</p>

        <p class="govuk-body">To report safeguarding concerns, call 0207 974 4444 (Monday to Friday, 9am to 5pm) and when prompted say "Safeguarding". If someone is in immediate danger, call 999.</p>

        <h2 class="govuk-heading-l">Before you make a referral</h2>

        <p class="govuk-body">This form is not for self-referral. If you want to ask for help for yourself, speak to your GP.</p>

        <p class="govuk-body">Before making a referral for someone else, there are 2 steps you should take first.</p>

        <h3 class="govuk-heading-m">Check they’re a Camden resident</h3>

        <p class="govuk-body">We can only accept referrals for Camden residents. Use the <a class="govuk-link" href="https://www.gov.uk/find-local-council">GOV.UK postcode checker</a> to check which local council the person you want to refer lives in.</p>

        <h3 class="govuk-heading-m">Get their details</h3>

        <p class="govuk-body">To refer someone, you need to know their:</p>

        <ul class="govuk-list govuk-list--bullet">
          <li>contact details</li>
          <li>date of birth</li>
          <li>address and living situation</li>
          <li>next of kin</li>
        </ul>

        <h2 class="govuk-heading-l">How to make a referral</h2>

        <p class="govuk-body">When making a referral, you should answer the questions in as much detail as you can.</p>

        <p class="govuk-body">If you need help filling the form in, call 0207 974 4444 (Monday to Friday, 9am to 5pm) and when prompted say "Adult Social Care".</p>

        <p class="govuk-body">Those who use British Sign Language can also <a class="govuk-link" href="https://www.camden.gov.uk/bsl-support-contact-camden">speak to us using SignVideo</a>.</p>

        {{ LBCamdenButton({
          text: "Make a referral",
          href: "/mental-health-referral/your-details",
          isStartButton: true
        }) }}

        <h3 class="govuk-heading-m">What happens next</h3>

        <p class="govuk-body">Your referral will be processed within 1 working day, then it’ll be triaged by the mental health social care team.</p>

        <p class="govuk-body">If you’ve requested we contact you first, we will do so using the contact details you’ve provided. Otherwise, we’ll contact the person you’ve referred. If they cannot be reached, we’ll contact you or their next of kin.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
{% endblock %}
